<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="/favicon-192x192.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="512x512" href="/favicon-512x512.png">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Contact — Norbert Barkah</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Get in touch with Mama Sue. Reach out about books, storytime, collaborations, speaking, or just to share a kind note.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="header-inner">
      <a href="index.html" class="site-logo"><img src="images/logo.jpg" alt="Norbert Barkah logo" class="header-logo"> Norbert <span>Barkah</span></a>
      <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
        <a href="index.html">Home</a>
        <a href="about.html">About</a>
        <a href="books.html">Books</a>
        <a href="enchanted-forest.html">Enchanted Forest</a>
        <a href="storytime.html">Storytime</a>
        <a href="press.html">Press</a>
        <a href="friends.html">Friends</a>
        <a href="testimonials.html">Testimonials</a>
                <a href="contact.html" class="active">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
      <p>Thank you for being here and for spending time in Norbert's world</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--cream);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-grid">
        
        <div class="fade-in">
          <h2>Send a Message</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">I'd love to hear from you. Whether you are reaching out about books, storytime, collaborations, speaking, or simply want to share a kind note, thank you for being here and for spending time in Norbert's world.</p>
          
          <form class="contact-form" name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/contact-success.html">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
            <p style="display:none;"><label>Do not fill this in: <input name="bot-field"></label></p>
            
            <label for="name">Your Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your name" required>
            
            <label for="email">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required>
            
            <label for="subject">What is this about?</label>
            <select id="subject" name="subject">
              <option value="">Choose one...</option>
              <option value="reader">Just saying hello</option>
              <option value="media">Media or interview inquiry</option>
              <option value="school">School, library, or event visit</option>
              <option value="collaboration">Collaboration or partnership</option>
              <option value="speaking">Speaking inquiry</option>
              <option value="other">Something else</option>
            </select>
            
            <label for="message">Your Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us what's on your mind..." required></textarea>
            
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Send Message</button>
              <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--sage-light); margin-top: 0.75rem;">For professional inquiries, event requests, collaborations, and reader notes.</p>
          </form>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in">
          <div class="contact-info-block">
            <h3>Other Ways to Connect</h3>
            
            <div class="contact-info-item">
              <h4>General Inquiries</h4>
              <p>info@norbertbarkah.com</p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-item">
              <h4>Media & Press</h4>
              <p>For interviews, features, and press requests, please include your outlet and deadline in your message.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-item">
              <h4>Schools & Libraries</h4>
              <p>Interested in a reading, visit, or virtual event? Let us know your school or organization, grade levels, and preferred dates.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-item">
              <h4>Speaking</h4>
              <p>For speaking inquiries, please share event details, audience, and timing in your message.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info-item">
              <h4>Follow Along</h4>
              <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">

                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/norbertbarkah/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram"
                   style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--forest-deep);">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                       stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/>
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4.5"/>
                    <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-family: var(--font-body);">Instagram</span>
                </a>

                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@norbertbarkah225" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="TikTok"
                   style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--forest-deep);">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                       stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M9 12a4 4 0 1 0 4 4V4a5 5 0 0 0 5 5"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-family: var(--font-body);">TikTok</span>
                </a>

                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@NorbertBarkah" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="YouTube"
                   style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--forest-deep);">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                       stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M22.54 6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.95-1.96C18.88 4 12 4 12 4s-6.88 0-8.59.46A2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.46 6.42 29 29 0 0 0 1 12a29 29 0 0 0 .46 5.58 2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.95 1.96C5.12 20 12 20 12 20s6.88 0 8.59-.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.96-1.96A29 29 0 0 0 23 12a29 29 0 0 0-.46-5.58z"/>
                    <polygon points="9.75 15.02 15.5 12 9.75 8.98 9.75 15.02" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-family: var(--font-body);">YouTube</span>
                </a>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="index.html" class="site-logo"><img src="images/logo.jpg" alt="Norbert Barkah logo" class="header-logo"> Norbert <span>Barkah</span></a>
          <p>Gentle stories of kindness, courage, and the quiet light that lives in all of us.</p>
          <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/norbertbarkah/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram">&#9679;</a>
            <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@norbertbarkah225" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="TikTok">&#9679;</a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@NorbertBarkah" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="YouTube">&#9679;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <h4>Explore</h4>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="books.html">Books</a></li>
            <li><a href="enchanted-forest.html">Enchanted Forest</a></li>
            <li><a href="storytime.html">Storytime</a>
        <a href="press.html">Press</a>
        <a href="friends.html">Friends</a></li>
            <li><a href="about.html">About</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <h4>Connect</h4>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="testimonials.html">Testimonials</a>
                <a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
            <li><a href="press.html">Press</a>
        <a href="friends.html">Friends</a></li>
